race.description: Community Bank Fleurieu Bendigo Bank Handicap (C1)
race.comment: REOFFER (7) dug deep to get off the mark last time at Oakbank in a strong maiden. Draws well again and can keep the ball rolling now. Leading player. OIE DE TOULOUSE (1) timed his run to perfection to get the verdict last time at Murray Bridge. Not drawn as kindly this time but is still improving and is worth following up, despite the big weight. STARNOVA (2) made the perfect returning when accounting for a maiden field at Oakbank last start. Sparingly raced and has more to offer. TOUGH TALK (5) won the lone fresh attempt and it came at this distance. Readied with two trials. Looking for a strong return.
